  | Lam of lam
  | Rel of int
  | Constant of constant
  | Ind of inductive
  | Sort of sorts
  | Var of identifier
  | App of lam * lam array
  | Const_int of int
  | Const_block of int * lam array
  | Case of lam * lam * lam array * case_info
  | Prod of name * lam * lam
  | Fix of name * rec_pos * lam * lam 

